title: [Vornavis, Peasant Holdings]
description: A large wheeled produce cart sits abandoned next to an irrigation pool.  Several wooden ladders and large wicker baskets lie strewn about the cart as if the pickers had fled the area in a rush.  An odd leathery sound seems to emanate from the shadowed boughs of the ancient apple trees.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, west, northwest
